According to official sources, 5 children of ages between 2 and 5
years have died of measles and several others affected by the disease
have been admitted to Miranshah District Headquarters.

The epidemic has been spreading in North Waziristan [Federally
Administered Tribal Areas] and other adjoining areas. People have
demanded the government provide treatment facilities at the hospital.

